%p
  The full list of payouts:

%table{style: 'width:100%; font-size:80%;'}
  %colgroup
    %col{style: 'width: 2em'}
    %col{style: 'width: 5em'}
    %col{style: 'width: 5em'}
    %col{style: ''}
    %col{style: 'width: 10em'}
  %thead
    %tr
      %th
        ID
      %th
        Wallet
      %th
        Amount
      %th
        Created
      %th
        Details
  %tbody
    - payouts.fetch(confirmed_user.login).each do |p|
      %tr
        %td
          = p['id']
        %td
          %code
            %a{href: "http://www.zold.io/ledger.html?wallet=#{p['wallet']}"}= p['wallet']
        %td
          = p['amount'].to_zld
        %td{title: Time.parse(c['created']).utc.iso8601}
          = Zold::Age.new(Time.parse(c['created']))
        %td
          = p['details']
